Junior Systems Administrator  
  
Based in Wynnum / Lytton area.  
  
An exciting permanent opportunity has become available to join this fast-
growing Engineering Company. Ideally suited to an all-round self-starter.  
  
A typical day looks like this:  

  * Responding to logged tickets for approximately 60-70 users, ensuring networks, systems, and data are active. 
  * Reviewing logs, health checks, backups etc. 
  * Technical support for all areas of business applications. 
  * Supporting O365, Windows Server and Azure AD. 
  * Various project work such as data migration. 
Qualifications required â€“  

  * Minimum 2 years of experience as a Systems Administrator. 
  * Experience with O365, Azure AD, backup software and Windows Server. 
  * Knowledge of VMWare, SharePoint, Single Sign On (SSO) and MFA would be an advantage however is not essential. 
  * High level of communication skills and literacy, as well as interpersonal skills. 
This is a varied role and you will be the single point of contact for this
line of the business. There will be a 2-3 month handover and training will be
provided. You will have access to escalated support.  
